snippet.title: Yoshi Goes to Tesco | RPG Maker Game | No Commentary
snippet.description:
Happy April Fools. (in Finland) Time to play a funny game from 2 years ago. I've never been to Tesco before so I assume this is accurate.

Game: Yoshi Goes to Tesco
Find the game here: https://frogge.itch.io/yoshi-tesco
Original creator: Frogge
Release Date: 2022
Engine: RPG Maker 2003
I do NOT own anything on this video, all credit to their respective creators.

If the creator wants me to take this down, please tell me.

uhh how do i record videos again uhh what is youtube. funny yoshi game. parody. funny. shitpost. uhh... april fools????????

Okay, okay jokes aside, happy april fools. I wanted to do something for April Fools and since I did want to make a video for this game at some point in my channel's life, why not now? There was an idea for me to do more for this, but it was too time-consuming and I'm tired. It's literally the day of April fools as I recorded this.

Who cares if I haven't uploaded in two months and return with a shitpost game, who cares. 

Peak game. A little funny game for this short time of year. I love a well-made shitpost. Especially ones made in RPG Maker because I'm biased. 

This technically is my 500 subs special too, but I will probably lose at least 200 of them after this so uhh...????? I dunno. 

Anyway I'm off to bed for the next 10 years. See ya then. Or not. I don't know what I'm doing anymore.

(Also apologies for being dumb and bad at the video game. It will happen again.)
